# Per-attempt provider logs the agent loop writes into the proof worktree.
# Ignored so they are never staged for check-in and do not trip the prove
# path guard (prove_target_only_changed), while remaining on disk for
# inspection in preserved --prove-local worktrees.
prove-attempt-*.log
